quran[21]{c,v,t,f}:
  53,49,"Dájúdájú Òun sì ni Olúwa ìràwọ̀ Ṣi‘rọ̄ (tí wọ́n sọ di òrìṣà)."
  53,50,"Dájúdájú Òun l’Ó pa ìran ‘Ād rẹ́, àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́;"
  53,51,"àti ìran Thamūd, kò sì ṣẹ́ wọn kù;"
  54,40,"Dájúdájú A ṣe al-Ƙur’ān ní ìrọ̀rùn fún ṣíṣe ìrántí. Ǹjẹ́ olùrántí wà báyìí bí?"
  54,41,"Dájúdájú àwọn ìkìlọ̀ dé bá àwọn ènìyàn Fir‘aon."
  54,42,"Wọ́n pe gbogbo àwọn āyah Wa ní irọ́ pátápátá. A sì gbá wọn mú ní ìgbámú (tí) Alágbára, Olùkápá (máa ń gbá ẹ̀dá mú)."
  55,34,"Nítorí náà, èwo nínú àwọn ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa ẹ̀yin ènìyàn àti àlùjànnú ni ẹ máa pè ní irọ́?"
  55,35,"Wọ́n máa ju ahọ́n iná àti èéfín (tàbí oje idẹ) iná lé ẹ̀yin méjèèjì lórí, ẹ̀yin méjèèjì kò sì níí lè ranra yín lọ́wọ́."
  55,36,"Nítorí náà, èwo nínú àwọn ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa ẹ̀yin ènìyàn àti àlùjànnú ni ẹ máa pè ní irọ́?"
  56,25,"Wọn kò níí gbọ́ ìsọkúsọ àti ọ̀rọ̀ ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ nínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra."
  56,26,"Àyàfi ọ̀rọ̀ àlàáfíà, àlàáfíà."
  56,27,"Àwọn èrò ọwọ́ ọtún, kí ni (ó máa ti dára tó fún) àwọn èrò ọwọ́ ọtún?"
  57,16,"Ṣé àkókò kò tí ì tó fún àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo pé kí ọkàn wọn rọ̀ fún ìrántí Allāhu àti ohun tó sọ̀kalẹ̀ nínú òdodo (ìyẹn, al-Ƙur’ān). Kí wọ́n sì má ṣe dà bí àwọn tí A fún ní Tírà ní ìṣáájú; ìgbà pẹ́ lórí wọn, ọkàn wọn bá le. Ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ nínú wọn sì ni òbìlẹ̀jẹ́."
  57,17,"Ẹ mọ̀ pé dájúdájú Allāhu l’Ó ń sọ ilẹ̀ di àyè lẹ́yìn tí ilẹ̀ ti kú. A kúkú ti ṣàlàyé àwọn āyah náá nítorí kí ẹ lè ṣe làákàyè."
  57,18,"Dájúdájú àwọn olùtọrẹ lọ́kùnrin àti àwọn olùtọrẹ lóbìnrin, tí wọ́n tún yá Allāhu ní dúkìá tó dára, (Allāhu) yóò ṣàdìpèlé rẹ̀ fún wọn. Ẹ̀san alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé sì wà fún wọn."
  58,10,"Dájúdájú ọ̀rọ̀ ìkọ̀kọ̀ (burúkú) ń wá láti ọ̀dọ̀ aṣ-Ṣaetọ̄n nítorí kí ó lè kó ìbànújẹ́ bá àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo. Kò sì lè fi kiní kan kó ìnira bá wọn àfi pẹ̀lú ìyọ̀ǹda Allāhu. Allāhu sì ni kí àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo gbáralé."
  58,11,"Ẹ̀yin tí ẹ gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, nígbà tí wọ́n bá sọ fún yín pé kí ẹ gbara yín láyè nínú àwọn ibùjókòó, ẹ gbara yín láyè. Allāhu yóò f’àyè gbà yín. Nígbà tí wọ́n bá sọ pé: “Ẹ dìde (síbi iṣẹ́ rere).” Ẹ dìde (sí i). Allāhu yóò ṣàgbéga àwọn ipò fún àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo àti àwọn tí A fún ní ìmọ̀ nínú yín. Allāhu sì ni Alámọ̀tán nípa ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́."
  58,12,"Ẹ̀yin tí ẹ gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, nígbà tí ẹ bá bá Òjíṣẹ́ sọ̀rọ̀ àtẹ̀sọ,{1} ẹ fi ọrẹ títa ṣíwájú ọ̀rọ̀ àtẹ̀sọ yín. Ìyẹn lóore jùlọ fún yín. Ó sì fọ̀ yín mọ́ jùlọ. Tí ẹ ò bá sì rí (ọrẹ), dájúdájú Allāhu ni Aláforíjìn, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run..",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Hujurọ̄t; 49:7.]
  59,1,"Ohunkóhun tó wà nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ohunkóhun tó wà nínú ilẹ̀ ń ṣàfọ̀mọ́ fún Allāhu. Òun sì ni Alágbára, Ọlọ́gbọ́n."
  59,2,"Òun ni Ẹni tí Ó mú àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú àwọn onítírà{1} jáde kúrò nínú ilé wọn fún àkọ́kọ́ àkójọ (wọ́n sínú ìlú Ṣām). Ẹ̀yin kò lérò pé wọn yóò jáde. Àwọn náà sì lérò pé dájúdájú àwọn odi ilé wọn yóò dáàbò bo àwọn lọ́dọ̀ Allāhu. Ṣùgbọ́n Allāhu wá bá wọn ní ibi tí wọn kò ti lérò; Allāhu sì ju ìbẹ̀rù sínú ọkàn wọn. Wọ́n ń fi ọwọ́ ara wọn àti ọwọ́ àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo wó àwọn ilé wọn. Nítorí náà, ẹ wòye, ẹ̀yin tí ẹ ní ojú ìríran..",footnotes:1:[Ìyẹn àwọn Yẹhudi ọmọ Nadīr.]
  59,3,"Àti pé tí kò bá jẹ́ pé Allāhu ti kọ ìjáde kúrò nínú ìlú Mọdīnah lé àwọn onítírà lórí ni, dájúdájú (Allāhu) ìbá jẹ wọ́n níyà nílé ayé. Ìyà Iná sì tún wà fún wọn ní ọ̀run.{1}.",footnotes:1:[Ìyẹn ni pé, tí àwọn onítírà kò bá fi ìlú Mọdīnah sílẹ̀ fún àwọn mùsùlùmí ni, ẹ̀mí wọn ìbá lọ sí i nítorí pé, wọ́n ti da àwọn mùsùlùmí.]
